  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the effect of a dentifrice containing L-ascorbic
      acid 2-phosphate magnesium salt on gingival inflammation, gingival bleeding and gingival
      redness.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
